<td tEditID="c1r2" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r2" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<font size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;">Dear&nbsp;</font><font face="arial" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;">{!Job_placement__c.Contact_Name__c},</font><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: center;"><font face="arial" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><b>Payment schedule for&nbsp;</b></font><font face="arial" size="2"><b>{!Job_placement__c.Wave__c}, clause 4.1</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: center;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;">Payment information for your employment contract with us on&nbsp;</font><font face="arial" size="2">{!Job_placement__c.Wave__c} is listed below. This information is subject to you completing your employment with us in conjunction with the conditions in your contract.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b>Payment overview</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2">You have been allocated to&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.Wave__c} as a&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.Role__c}.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2">You are contracted to work on the NCS programme from&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.Assignment_start_date__c} to&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.Assignment_end_date__c} ("Work Period"), with&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.Annual_Leave_entitlement__c} days ("<b>Holiday Period</b>")] together referred to as a Wave Contract (a "<b>Wave Contract</b>").</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2">You will be paid an amount of {!Job_placement__c.Total_gross_pay__c}.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b>Staff working NCS: Real Challenge Action (November weekends)</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2">If your role is also required to work NCS: Real Challenge Action (NCS: RCA), you will be contracted to work two weekend dates in November.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">You will be paid the daily rate as agreed with your Staffing Team for each weekend date you work ("Work Period") plus</font><font size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</font><font size="2">{!Job_placement__c.RCA_Annual_Leave_entitlement__c}&nbsp;days ("<b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Holiday Period</b>")], together referred to as a Weekend Contract (a "<b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Weekend Contract</b>").</font></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2">This additional amount will be paid to you on <b>17/12/15.</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2">The NCS: RCA weekend dates take place on <b>Saturday 14 November</b>&nbsp;and <b>Saturday 21 November</b>.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2">All payment amounts are calculated on the basis that you will work all days required of your role; any days of half days that you are absent or no longer required to work will be deducted from your pay.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2">All of your pay will be subject to tax and National Insurance (NI) deductions. You will be able to review tax deductions on your payslip which is sent to you via email two days prior to your payment date. The Challenge is unable to answer or help with any tax queries; if you are concerned about your tax code, please contact HMRC directly.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2"><b>When will I receive this payment?</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;">You will be paid for your role on&nbsp;</font><font face="arial" size="2">{!Job_placement__c.Wave__c} on&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c}.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2">We pay our seasonal staff on a monthly basis, and aim to pay within 5 weeks of their completing a wave (where possible). For an overview of our Autumn payment dates please see <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/Autumnpaymentdates_(2).pdf">this document</a>.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b>What next?</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2">You will receive a 'Payment Notification' email outlining your approved pay at the end of your wave. If you are working over the NCS: RCA November dates, you will receive a separate payment notification email for each individual date you work.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b>Workplace pension auto-enrollment: </b>Due to new auto-enrollment legislation, employees of The Challenge, including a small number of seasonal staff, will be enrolled into a workplace pension scheme. Auto-enrollment does not occur until October 2015 and staff will have the opportunity to opt-out at this point. To see if you qualify for auto-enrollment, please see our <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/frequently-asked-questions/">FAQs</a>.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b>Any questions?</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="arial" size="2">If you have any questions about the payment schedule please contact your <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/contact/">local staffing team</a>. Alternatively, you can find information on the Autumn programme and the payment process on our <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/frequently-asked-questions/">FAQs</a>.</font></div>]]></td>
</tr>
